<item>
            <title>[SOLR-2793] A SolrIndexSearcher can be left open if the executor rejects a task.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-2793</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This is starting to really bug me because tests almost never pass on my linux box due to this issue. Time to fix it.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12524580">SOLR-2793</key>
            <summary>A SolrIndexSearcher can be left open if the executor rejects a task.</summary>
